  * [x86] i2c: Enable I2C_ISMT, I2C_DESIGNWARE_PCI as modules
  * [x86] mouse: Enable MOUSE_CYAPA as modules
  * [armel/{iop32x,ixp4xx,orion5x}] Disable features to reduce kernel size
    - Disable KSM, YAMA
    - [armel/orion5x] Disable FTRACE

